original_question:
\[f(n) = \left\{
\begin{array}{cl}
\lfloor n \rfloor & \text{ if }n \geq 4, \\
\lceil n \rceil & \text{ if } n < 4.
\end{array}
\right.\] मान्नुहोस् $f\left(\frac{\pi}{3}\right) + f(\sqrt{45}) + f(8^{2/3})$ पत्ता लगाउनुहोस्।

